# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:22
translate spanish main18_50df7566:

    # "My phone buzzes in my pocket. Whitney's calling."
    "Mi teléfono vibra en el bolsillo. Es Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:26
translate spanish main18_0b8efa0c:

    # pc "Hey, Whitney."
    pc "Hola, Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:28
translate spanish main18_b3780b43:

    # wt "Could you come over to the lab? There have been some developments on our project."
    wt "¿Podrías venir al laboratorio? Ha habido novedades en nuestro proyecto."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:29
translate spanish main18_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:30
translate spanish main18_a1cf6718:

    # wt "Good. See you soon."
    wt "Bien. Nos vemos pronto."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:32
translate spanish main18_70aad62d:

    # "She hangs up before I can say anything else. I drive to her house, not really knowing what to expect."
    "Cuelga antes de que pueda decir nada más. Conduzco hasta su casa, sin saber muy bien qué esperar."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:35
translate spanish main18_642e548e:

    # "When I walk in, Whitney greets me with a smile."
    "Cuando entro, Whitney me recibe con una sonrisa."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:36
translate spanish main18_84c2c4d9:

    # wt "I think that today is the day."
    wt "Creo que hoy es el día."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:37
translate spanish main18_f1af214e:

    # pc "I'm going through the hoop today?"
    pc "¿Hoy voy a pasar por el aro?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:38
translate spanish main18_9b21c179:

    # wt "Oh... no, not that day."
    wt "Oh... no, hoy no."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:39
translate spanish main18_163afad6:

    # wt "But I did send something through earlier and I have very high expectations about it returning right-side out this time."
    wt "Pero he enviado algo antes y tengo muchas esperanzas de que esta vez salga del otro lado sin dar la vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:42
translate spanish main18_bf4bae4a:

    # pc "What did you send through?"
    pc "¿Qué has enviado?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:43
translate spanish main18_8862260f:

    # wt "A dog."
    wt "Un perro."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:46
translate spanish main18_33869dd5:

    # pc "Oh, fuck no! What happened to that mouse was bad enough!"
    pc "¡Joder, no! ¡Lo que le pasó a ese ratón ya fue bastante malo!"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:47
translate spanish main18_68028f15:

    # pc "I don't need to see a cute little doggo like that!"
    pc "¡No necesito ver a un perrito tan monito como ese!"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:48
translate spanish main18_a4389d75:

    # wt "It's going to be fine. I fixed that problem."
    wt "No pasa nada. He solucionado ese problema."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:51
translate spanish main18_0e0fdef8:

    # wt "It's time. Come on, let's watch."
    wt "Es la hora. Venga, vamos a verlo."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:52
translate spanish main18_227693cf:

    # pc "I'm not looking."
    pc "No voy a mirar."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:55
translate spanish main18_40bce766:

    # "There's a bright light that envelops the lab."
    "Una luz brillante envuelve el laboratorio."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:56
translate spanish main18_6b94c821:

    # pc "Tell me when it's over. I can't look."
    pc "Avísame cuando haya terminado. No puedo mirar."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:59
translate spanish main18_966430c1:

    # "Then the light goes away and a dog lets out a sharp little bark."
    "Entonces la luz se desvanece y un perro suelta un ladrido agudo."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:60
translate spanish main18_1ce5c850:

    # wt "See, it's back! No problem!"
    wt "¡Ves, ha vuelto! ¡No hay problema!"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:61
translate spanish main18_ce4595e5:

    # pc "Is its body inside out or his head on backwards or anything?"
    pc "¿Tiene el cuerpo del revés o la cabeza al revés o algo así?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:62
translate spanish main18_239335b7:

    # wt "No it looks normal."
    wt "No, parece normal."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:63
translate spanish main18_8b0e0eb7:

    # wt "Its eyes are going in two different directions, but I'm fairly certain it was like that before going through the portal."
    wt "Sus ojos miran en dos direcciones diferentes, pero estoy bastante seguro de que ya era así antes de atravesar el portal."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:66
translate spanish main18_22113cb6:

    # "I turn around and bend down to pet the dog, looking her over for any deformities."
    "Me doy la vuelta y me agacho para acariciar a la perrita, examinándola en busca de cualquier deformidad."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:67
translate spanish main18_8a39fdca:

    # pc "I'm so glad that nothing happened to her."
    pc "Me alegro mucho de que no le haya pasado nada."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:68
translate spanish main18_67773b18:

    # pc "Did she really go to another world?"
    pc "¿De verdad se fue a otro mundo?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:69
translate spanish main18_7c999901:

    # wt "Yes, she did."
    wt "Sí, así es."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:70
translate spanish main18_5e058906:

    # wt "I'll need to run some vitals on her, but it looks like we were successful."
    wt "Tendré que tomarle las constantes vitales, pero parece que lo hemos conseguido."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:71
translate spanish main18_9de37a73:

    # wt "Finally."
    wt "Por fin."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:74
translate spanish main18_df4dc28b:

    # "The dog runs over and jumps onto her lap, quickly making herself comfortable."
    "La perra corre hacia ella y salta a su regazo, poniéndose rápidamente cómoda."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:75
translate spanish main18_770c63b8:

    # pc "What are you going to do with her now?"
    pc "¿Qué vas a hacer con ella ahora?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:76
translate spanish main18_6d4e8977:

    # wt "I'll feed her and monitor her to make sure she's healthy."
    wt "Le daré de comer y la vigilaré para asegurarme de que está sana."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:77
translate spanish main18_b1f075a8:

    # pc "What's her name?"
    pc "¿Cómo se llama?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:78
translate spanish main18_2dec4e90:

    # wt "Test Subject 9."
    wt "Sujeto de prueba 9."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:79
translate spanish main18_2ff3af31:

    # pc "Nine? You went through eight others then?"
    pc "¿Nueve? ¿Entonces has pasado por otros ocho?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:80
translate spanish main18_61c11568:

    # wt "Let's not talk about those."
    wt "No hablemos de eso."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:83
translate spanish main18_0ecec7f7:

    # wt "The point is that we were successful."
    wt "Lo importante es que hemos tenido éxito."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:84
translate spanish main18_702e06d9:

    # wt "This was my last test. I believe that we are now ready for you to go."
    wt "Esta era mi última prueba. Creo que ya estamos listos para que te vayas."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:85
translate spanish main18_d5ce9d5a:

    # pc "So I can go through the portal and find my dad?"
    pc "¿Así que puedo atravesar el portal y encontrar a mi padre?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:86
translate spanish main18_b1f1155f:

    # wt "Yes. It's ready and it's safe. As safe as I can make it, anyway."
    wt "Sí. Está listo y es seguro. Tan seguro como puedo hacerlo, al menos."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:89
translate spanish main18_c0960aa3:

    # wt "I'll just do the final touches on everything. Starting tomorrow, we can go whenever you're ready. Just give me a call."
    wt "Solo daré los últimos retoques a todo. A partir de mañana, podemos irnos cuando estés listo. Solo llámame."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:90
translate spanish main18_58040817:

    # wt "I'd recommend doing anything that you want to get done {i}before{/i} you go through the portal, though."
    wt "Aunque te recomiendo que hagas todo lo que quieras hacer {i}antes{/i} de atravesar el portal."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:93
translate spanish main18_8b77f81f:

    # wt "I've done everything I can to make sure that it is safe for you, but you're still traveling to a different universe."
    wt "He hecho todo lo posible para asegurarme de que sea seguro para ti, pero sigues viajando a un universo diferente."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:94
translate spanish main18_21510b56:

    # wt "Unforeseen things could occur."
    wt "Podrían ocurrir cosas imprevistas."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:95
translate spanish main18_32218263:

    # wt "So make sure you're really ready to do it."
    wt "Así que asegúrate de que estás realmente lista para hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:98
translate spanish main18_6199dfa8:

    # wt "And, [pcname], it's okay if you don't want to go."
    wt "Y, [pcname], no pasa nada si no quieres ir."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:99
translate spanish main18_78a6f4d0:

    # wt "You don't have to. Even though I built this thing, I would be perfectly happy never sending you through it."
    wt "No tienes por qué hacerlo. Aunque yo haya construido esto, estaría perfectamente feliz sin enviarte nunca a través de él."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:102
translate spanish main18_ea1168de:

    # pc "Thanks, Whitney."
    pc "Gracias, Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:103
translate spanish main18_b35ddc8a:

    # pc "But no... I have to go."
    pc "Pero no... Tengo que irme."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:104
translate spanish main18_23271d25:

    # pc "I mean, this is the whole reason I came home in the first place. To find my dad."
    pc "Quiero decir, esta es la única razón por la que volví a casa en primer lugar. Para encontrar a mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:105
translate spanish main18_0452074c:

    # pc "I can't just ignore that and give up now. I have to finish this."
    pc "No puedo simplemente ignorar eso y rendirme ahora. Tengo que terminar esto."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:106
translate spanish main18_f7892b7b:

    # wt "Well, whenever you are ready to go, let me know."
    wt "Bueno, cuando estés lista para irte, avísame."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:109
translate spanish main18_5c46d16d:

    # wt "No rush though."
    wt "Pero no hay prisa."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:110
translate spanish main18_6901e1e1:

    # wt "I'll keep running tests. We want it to be as safe as possible."
    wt "Seguiré haciendo pruebas. Queremos que sea lo más seguro posible."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:111
translate spanish main18_4996446d:

    # pc "Great! I'll see you later then, Whitney."
    pc "¡Genial! Nos vemos luego, Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:112
translate spanish main18_cb56553f:

    # "Nine" "Arf!"
    "Nine" "¡Arf!"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:115
translate spanish main18_c347d659:

    # "I leave Whitney's and drive back towards town."
    "Salgo de casa de Whitney y conduzco de vuelta hacia la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:124
translate spanish main18b_87e78e2e:

    # pc "I'm ready to go through the portal."
    pc "Estoy lista para atravesar el portal."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:126
translate spanish main18b_5ea619be:

    # rj "Hey, hold on just a second."
    rj "Oye, espera un momento."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:127
translate spanish main18b_a7b8c7c5:

    # rj "Really make sure you're ready to do this before agreeing to it, okay?"
    rj "Asegúrate de que estás lista para hacer esto antes de aceptar, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:129
translate spanish main18b_6a52ca86:

    # rj "After you agree to go through the portal, there is no turning back."
    rj "Una vez que aceptes atravesar el portal, no habrá vuelta atrás."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:130
translate spanish main18b_2e26d408:

    # rj "You will not be able to access the replay menus or do any scenes that you might be missing with the characters."
    rj "No podrás acceder a los menús de repetición ni realizar ninguna escena que te hayas perdido con los personajes."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:131
translate spanish main18b_6ac8b824:

    # rj "So make sure you have saved, and be sure you've done everything you want to do with the characters you are interested in."
    rj "Así que asegúrate de haber guardado y de haber hecho todo lo que quieras hacer con los personajes que te interesan."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:133
translate spanish main18b_5c5d3cda:

    # rj "Also make sure all the characters that you're interested in have their hearts turned on!"
    rj "¡Asegúrate también de que todos los personajes que te interesan tengan el corazón activado!"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:136
translate spanish main18b_7ffada8d:

    # wt "Are you sure? Once you do this, everything is going to change."
    wt "¿Estás segura? Una vez que hagas esto, todo va a cambiar."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:142
translate spanish main18b_434f897c:

    # wt "That's okay. I'm not really ready either. Let's do it another time."
    wt "No pasa nada. Yo tampoco estoy del todo preparada. Hagámoslo en otra ocasión."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:143
translate spanish main18b_f7fdb754:

    # wt "Just let me know when you're sure."
    wt "Avísame cuando estés segura."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:144
translate spanish main18b_e55fa572:

    # pc "Okay. Talk to you later, Whitney."
    pc "Vale. Hablamos luego, Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:146
translate spanish main18b_b645e144:

    # pc "I'm ready. I have to make that jump at some point."
    pc "Estoy lista. Tengo que dar ese salto en algún momento."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:148
translate spanish main18b_49bdea02:

    # wt "I suppose you do."
    wt "Supongo que sí."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:149
translate spanish main18b_1cb6997c:

    # wt "I'll get things started. See you when you get here."
    wt "Voy a ponerlo en marcha. Nos vemos cuando llegues."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:152
translate spanish main18b_d00c4087:

    # "We hang up and I drive over to Whitney's lab."
    "Colgamos y conduzco hasta el laboratorio de Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:156
translate spanish main18b_f96bbf7a:

    # wt "I've tested everything I can test. We are good to go."
    wt "He probado todo lo que se podía probar. Estamos listos para empezar."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:157
translate spanish main18b_53248501:

    # wt "Let me tell you how this is going to work."
    wt "Déjame explicarte cómo va a funcionar esto."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:160
translate spanish main18b_64dd1ef1:

    # wt "You have to wear this. There are diamonds in it that will power the hoop and it will help me find your DNA signature to bring you back."
    wt "Tienes que llevar esto puesto. Contiene diamantes que alimentarán el aro y me ayudarán a encontrar tu firma de ADN para traerte de vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:161
translate spanish main18b_6d5a9291:

    # wt "It separates into two, so you can give one to your father as well and I can bring both of you back."
    wt "Se divide en dos, así que puedes darle uno a tu padre también y así podré traeros a los dos de vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:162
translate spanish main18b_59d33331:

    # pc "What do I have to do to get back once I'm over there?"
    pc "¿Qué tengo que hacer para volver una vez que esté allí?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:165
translate spanish main18b_e92eca3e:

    # wt "You don't have to do anything except wear the bracelet. I'll do everything from my end."
    wt "No tienes que hacer nada, salvo llevar el brazalete. Yo me encargaré de todo por mi parte."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:166
translate spanish main18b_93470657:

    # wt "I am going to give you a day, then I'm going to start trying to bring you back."
    wt "Te voy a dar un día, y luego empezaré a intentar traerte de vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:167
translate spanish main18b_91030856:

    # wt "Time may work differently over there. I attempted to send a clock through, but when it came back, it was no longer functioning."
    wt "Puede que el tiempo funcione de forma diferente allí. Intenté enviar un reloj, pero cuando volvió, ya no funcionaba."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:168
translate spanish main18b_f198fd64:

    # wt "So, I'm not sure how long it will feel like over there for you, but it will be a day here."
    wt "Así que no estoy segura de cuánto tiempo os parecerá que estáis allí, pero aquí será un día."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:171
translate spanish main18b_dc3f47da:

    # wt "Just do not lose the bracelet. If you do, I won't be able to find you."
    wt "Simplemente no perdáis la pulsera. Si lo hacéis, no podré encontraros."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:172
translate spanish main18b_238bde54:

    # pc "Got it."
    pc "Entendido."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:175
translate spanish main18b_b5f45329:

    # wt "For that reason, I built a cloaking device on the bracelet that only works while it's being worn."
    wt "Por esa razón, he incorporado un dispositivo de camuflaje en la pulsera que solo funciona mientras se lleva puesta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:176
translate spanish main18b_25601f60:

    # wt "It would be very bad if somebody saw it and mugged you or something."
    wt "Sería muy malo que alguien la viera y os asaltara o algo así."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:179
translate spanish main18b_7ba53a6c:

    # "She presses a button on the bracelet and it disappears from my wrist."
    "Ella pulsa un botón de la pulsera y esta desaparece de mi muñeca."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:180
translate spanish main18b_1f4a5264:

    # pc "Wow, I can still feel it, but it's completely invisible. You can make things invisible?"
    pc "Vaya, todavía la noto, pero es completamente invisible. ¿Puedes hacer que las cosas sean invisibles?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:181
translate spanish main18b_c858afbd:

    # wt "Obviously."
    wt "Obviamente."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:182
translate spanish main18b_afbf2643:

    # wt "There's only two buttons. One to toggle the cloaking and one to separate the bracelets. You'll feel them."
    wt "Solo hay dos botones. Uno para activar el camuflaje y otro para separar las pulseras. Los notarás."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:185
translate spanish main18b_a80ec8cc:

    # pc "So go through, find Dad, split the bracelets, give him one and wait for you to pull us back."
    pc "Así que atraviesa el portal, busca a papá, separa las pulseras, dale una a él y espera a que nos traigas de vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:186
translate spanish main18b_fb5d9627:

    # wt "That's it."
    wt "Eso es todo."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:189
translate spanish main18b_1a938003:

    # wt "Oh, one more thing. You must also raise your heart rate before going through the portal."
    wt "Ah, una cosa más. También debes aumentar tu frecuencia cardíaca antes de atravesar el portal."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:190
translate spanish main18b_bfbcace7:

    # wt "You need your heart rate up, or the transfer process could make you go into cardiac arrest."
    wt "Necesitas que tu frecuencia cardíaca suba, o el proceso de transferencia podría provocarte un paro cardíaco."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:191
translate spanish main18b_6f6a186f:

    # wt "Your father anticipated this and used methamphetamine to raise his heart rate."
    wt "Tu padre lo previó y utilizó metanfetamina para aumentar su frecuencia cardíaca."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:194
translate spanish main18b_19bb4fb3:

    # wt "I have no idea why he would resort to that. There are much easier ways to raise your heart rate, before resorting to a chemical solution."
    wt "No tengo ni idea de por qué recurriría a eso. Hay formas mucho más fáciles de aumentar la frecuencia cardíaca antes de recurrir a una solución química."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:195
translate spanish main18b_5161d426:

    # wt "You could run in place. You could do jumping jacks."
    wt "Podrías correr sin moverte del sitio. Podrías hacer saltos de tijera."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:198
translate spanish main18b_973e471b:

    # wt "But personally, I suggest intercourse."
    wt "Pero, personalmente, te sugiero el coito."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:199
translate spanish main18b_c87c6119:

    # pc "Intercourse?"
    pc "¿El coito?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:200
translate spanish main18b_f4d98192:

    # wt "Sex. Vigorous sex."
    wt "Sexo. Sexo vigoroso."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:201
translate spanish main18b_dae505a2:

    # wt "It will raise your heart rate, plus the release of endorphins will help make the transition between worlds more smooth."
    wt "Aumentará tu frecuencia cardíaca y, además, la liberación de endorfinas ayudará a que la transición entre mundos sea más suave."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:204
translate spanish main18b_4de3d598:

    # pc "Sex... with you?"
    pc "¿Sexo... contigo?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:206
translate spanish main18b_29859d1a:

    # wt "Unless there is someone else you would prefer."
    wt "A menos que haya alguien más con quien prefieras hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:208
translate spanish main18b_df1b9bcb:

    # wt "No, of course not with me."
    wt "No, claro que no conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:209
translate spanish main18b_b0acc711:

    # wt "You can call whoever you'd like. I don't mind. I'll turn the other way."
    wt "Puedes llamar a quien quieras. No me importa. Me daré la vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:261
translate spanish main18lisa_84922f36:

    # pc "Hi, [mom]. I have something weird to ask you, but can you trust me?"
    pc "Hola, [mom]. Tengo que preguntarte algo raro, pero ¿puedes confiar en mí?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:262
translate spanish main18lisa_7ce145d0:

    # sp "Sure, honey. I trust you."
    sp "Claro, cariño. Confío en ti."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:263
